trans-unit.source: Defines the different language versions of the Gregorian calendar.
trans-unit.target: Definiuje różne wersje językowe kalendarza gregoriańskiego.

trans-unit.source: The date and time patterns associated with the <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> vary depending on the language.
trans-unit.target: Data i godzina wzorce skojarzone z <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>się różnić w zależności od języka.</xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> is selected in <xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, GregorianCalendarTypes can be used to specify which date and time patterns to use in that <xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo>.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>wybrano <xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, GregorianCalendarTypes może być używany do określenia, które wzorców daty i godziny do użycia w tym <xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo>.</xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo> </xref:System.Globalization.DateTimeFormatInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>

trans-unit.source: For Arabic cultures, more language versions of the Gregorian calendar are available.
trans-unit.target: Arabski kultur więcej wersji językowych kalendarza gregoriańskiego są dostępne.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can use the French version of <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> using the MiddleEastFrench value.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład można użyć wersji z językiem francuskim <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>przy użyciu wartości MiddleEastFrench.</xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>

trans-unit.source: A culture that supports <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> might not support all language versions of <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>.
trans-unit.target: Kultura, która obsługuje <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>mogą nie obsługiwać wszystkich wersji językowych <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>.</xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.OptionalCalendars%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties specify the calendars supported by that culture.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>i <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.OptionalCalendars%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości określają kalendarzy obsługiwany przez ten kultury.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.OptionalCalendars%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.Calendar%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> is supported, <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar.CalendarType%2A> can be used to determine which language versions of <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> are supported.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>jest obsługiwana, <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar.CalendarType%2A>może służyć do określenia wersjach językowych programu <xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>są obsługiwane.</xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar> </xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar.CalendarType%2A> </xref:System.Globalization.GregorianCalendar>
